"logo","塑身衣"],"title":"logo-塑身衣"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"哈博药业外贸网站logo logo构成 “H”-Healthy健康\n“A”-Aurora曙光,朝霞\n“B”-Beloved爱的人\n“O”-Oomph精力充沛\n“🌄”-朝阳,希望\nlogo释义 HABO四字母连在一起的意思可以解释为:希望我爱的人健康如意,元气满满,生命犹如朝霞之灿烂。\nHABO号召语 Care With No Words。中文意思是关爱无声。换句话说HABO公司希望用产品质量说话来关爱每一位客户。\n效果展示 -End","date":"2019-09-01T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://junxinjay.netlify.app/zh/blog/logo-habo/","tags":["logo","habo"],"title":"logo-habo"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"End","date":"2019-08-01T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://junxinjay.netlify.app/zh/blog/%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5/","tags":["首页","活动"],"title":"活动首页"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"End","date":"2019-07-01T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://junxinjay.netlify.app/zh/blog/%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5/","tags":["首页","日常"],"title":"日常首页"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"塑身衣 -End","date":"2019-03-01T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://junxinjay.netlify.app/zh/blog/%E8%AF%A6%E6%83%85%E9%A1%B5-%E6%9C%8D%E9%A5%B0%E7%B1%BB/","tags":["详情页","服饰"],"title":"详情页-服饰类"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"筋膜枪 智能锁 -End","date":"2019-02-01T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://junxinjay.netlify.app/zh/blog/%E8%AF%A6%E6%83%85%E9%A1%B5-3c%E7%B1%BB/","tags":["详情页","3C"],"title":"详情页-3C类"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"钙铁锌硒咀嚼片 这是一款青少年以及儿童食用的钙铁锌硒咀嚼片，整个详情页用了产品包装色-绿色，让详情页整体具有统一感和协调感，在创意上用了符合产品调性的梦想宇航员作为背景去烘托表现产品给人带来一种的童真的，梦想实现的感觉。\n凝胶糖果 牛磺酸片 坚果 End","date":"2019-01-01T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://junxinjay.netlify.app/zh/blog/%E8%AF%A6%E6%83%85%E9%A1%B5-%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E7%B1%BB/","tags":["详情页","食品"],"title":"详情页-食品类"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"平面海报 -End","date":"2018-09-01T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://junxinjay.netlify.app/zh/blog/%E6%B5%B7%E6%8A%A5-%E5%8C%BB%E7%BE%8E%E7%B1%BB-/","tags":["海报","医美"],"title":"海报-医美类"},{"author":"君心Jay","categories":null,"contents":"塑身衣PC海报 End","date":"2018-08-01T00:00:00Z","per